ns";s:5:"price";s:10:"&#36;49.00";}i:49;O:8:"stdClass":5:{s:5:"title";s:13:"Limited Deals";s:5:"image";s:0:"";s:7:"excerpt";s:111:"Offer expiring deals to your customers and optionally display order totals & savings via a stylish css3 banner.";s:4:"link";s:108:"https://www.woothemes.com/products/limited-deals/?utm_source=product&utm_medium=upsell&utm_campaign=wcaddons";s:5:"price";s:10:"&#36;49.00";}i:50;O:8:"stdClass":5:{s:5:"title";s:23:"Inspire Payment Gateway";s:5:"image";s:85:"https://www.woothemes.com/wp-content/uploads/woocommerce_uploads/2012/11/logo.200.png";s:7:"excerpt";s:145:"Inspire Commerce is the all-in-one solution that allows you to turn your beautiful WooCommerce backed shopping experience into a selling machine.";s:4:"link";s:112:"https://www.woothemes.com/products/inspire-gateway-2/?utm_source=product&utm_medium=upsell&utm_campaign=wcaddons";s:5:"price";s:9:"&#36;0.00";}i:51;O:8:"stdClass":5:{s:5:"title";s:24:"Accepted Payment Methods";s:5:"image";s:0:"";s:7:"excerpt";s:93:"Allows you to display which payment methods you accept via widget, shortcode or template tag.";s:4:"link";s:119:"https://www.woothemes.com/products/accepted-payment-methods/?utm_source=product&utm_medium=upsell&utm_campaign=wcaddons";s:5:"price";s:9:"&#36;0.00";}i:52;O:8:"stdClass":5:{s:5:"title";s:14:"IcePay Gateway";s:5:"image";s:0:"";s:7:"excerpt";s:118:"ICEPAY online payment plugin for WooCommerce provides all popular online payment methods for your WooCommerce webshop.";s:4:"link";s:109:"https://www.woothemes.com/products/icepay-gateway/?utm_source=product&utm_medium=upsell&utm_campaign=wcaddons";s:5:"price";s:9:"&#36;0.00";}i:53;O:8:"stdClass":5:{s:5:"title";s:25:"Improvely for WooCommerce";s:5:"image";s:0:"";s:7:"excerpt";s:141:"Use Improvely with your WooCommerce-powered store to measure your advertising, click fraud marketing, social media marketing and SEO results.";s:4:"link";s:120:"https://www.woothemes.com/products/improvely-for-woocommerce/?utm_source=product&utm_medium=upsell&utm_campaign=wcaddons";s:5:"price";s:9:"&#36;0.00";}i:54;O:8:"stdClass":5:{s:5:"title";s:14:"Bring Shipping";s:5:"image";s:82:"https://www.woothemes.com/wp-content/uploads/woocommerce_uploads/2012/10/bring.png";s:7:"excerpt";s:104:"Automatically calculate shipment prices of products in your customer''s cart using the services of Bring.";s:4:"link";s:109:"https://www.woothemes.com/products/bring-shipping/?utm_source=product&utm_medium=upsell&utm_campaign=wcaddons";s:5:"price";s:10:"&#36;79.00";}i:55;O:8:"stdClass":5:{s:5:"title";s:17:"Amazon Simple Pay";s:5:"image";s:82:"https://www.woothemes.com/wp-content/uploads/woocommerce_uploads/2012/08/home.jpeg";s:7:"excerpt";s:62:"Take payments on your WooCommerce store via Amazon Simple Pay.";s:4:"link";s:111:"https://www.woothemes.com/?post_type=product&p=18725&utm_source=product&utm_medium=upsell&utm_campaign=wcaddons";s:5:"price";s:10:"&#36;79.00";}i:56;O:8:"stdClass":5:{s:5:"title";s:14:"QuickBooks POS";s:5:"image";s:0:"";s:7:"excerpt";s:68:"Streamline your order and inventory management using QuickBooks POS.";s:4:"link";s:109:"https://www.woothemes.com/products/quickbooks-pos/?utm_source=product&utm_medium=upsell&utm_campaign=wcaddons";s:5:"price";s:11:"&#36;129.00";}i:57;O:8:"stdClass":5:{s:5:"title";s:22:"QuickBooks Integration";s:5:"image";s:0:"";s:7:"excerpt";s:64:"Sync orders, customers and inventory to your QuickBooks software";s:4:"link";s:111:"https://www.woothemes.com/?post_type=product&p=18658&utm_source=product&utm_medium=upsell&utm_campaign=wcaddons";s:5:"price";s:11:"&#36;129.00";}i:58;O:8:"stdClass":5:{s:5:"title";s:11:"PayJunction";s:5:"image";s:68:"https://www.woothemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/payjunction.jpg";s:7:"excerpt";s:108:"Accept all major brands with the PayJunction service: Visa, MasterCard, American Express, Discover and more.";s:4:"link";s:111:"https://www.woothemes.com/?post_type=product&p=18656&utm_source=product&utm_medium=upsell&utm_campaign=wcaddons";s:5:"price";s:9:"&#36;0.00";}i:59;O:8:"stdClass":5:{s:5:"title";s:16:"Pinterest Button";s:5:"image";s:0:"";s:7:"excerpt";s:158:"Easily add a Pinterest Pin-it button to your WooCommerce single product pages. This allows customers to easily post your product images directly to Pinterest.";s:4:"link";s:111:"https://www.woothemes.com/products/pinterest-button/?utm_source=product&utm_medium=upsell&utm_campaign=wcaddons";s:5:"price";s:9:"&#36;0.00";}i:60;O:8:"stdClass":5:{s:5:"title";s:24:"Sequential Order Numbers";s:5:"image";s:0:"";s:7:"excerpt";s:105:"This plugin extends the WooCommerce e-commerce plugin by setting sequential order numbers for new orders.";s:4:"link";s:119:"https://www.woothemes.com/products/sequential-order-numbers/?utm_source=product&utm_medium=upsell&utm_campaign=wcaddons";s:5:"price";s:9:"&#36;0.00";}i:61;O:8:"stdClass":5:{s:5:"title";s:17:"WP Cart Mailcheck";s:5:"image";s:0:"";s:7:"excerpt";s:102:"Checks for mis-spelled email addresses (e.g. joe.bloggs@gnail.com) and corrects them for the customer.";s:4:"link";s:112:"https://www.woothemes.com/products/wp-cart-mailcheck/?utm_source=product&utm_medium=upsell&utm_campaign=wcaddons";s:5:"price";s:9:"&#36;0.00";}i:62;O:8:"stdClass":5:{s:5:"title";s:18:"Admin Bar Addition";s:5:"image";s:0:"";s:7:"excerpt";s:127:"This plugin adds useful admin links and massive resources for the WooCommerce Shop Plugin to the WordPress Toolbar / Admin Bar.";s:4:"link";s:113:"https://www.woothemes.com/products/admin-bar-addition/?utm_source=product&utm_medium=upsell&utm_campaign=wcaddons";s:5:"price";s:9:"&#36;0.00";}i:63;O:8:"stdClass":5:{s:5:"title";s:15:"Genesis Connect";s:5:"image";s:0:"";s:7:"excerpt";s:111:"This plugin allows you to seamlessly integrate WooCommerce with the Genesis Framework and Genesis child themes.";s:4:"link";s:110:"https://www.woothemes.com/products/genesis-connect/?utm_source=product&utm_medium=upsell&utm_campaign=wcaddons";s:5:"price";s:9:"&#36;0.00";}i:64;O:8:"stdClass":5:{s:5:"title";s:14:"Delivery Notes";s:5:"image";s:0:"";s:7:"excerpt";s:142:"Print order invoices & delivery notes for WooCommerce shop. You can add company/shop info as well as personal notes & policies to print pages.";s:4:"link";s:109:"https://www.woothemes.com/products/delivery-notes/?utm_source=product&utm_medium=upsell&utm_campaign=wcaddons";s:5:"price";s:9:"&#36;0.00";}i:65;O:8:"stdClass":5:{s:5:"title";s:25:"Postgiro/Bankgiro gateway";s:5:"image";s:0:"";s:7:"excerpt";s:136:"Adds a new payment gateway to WooCommerce, there you are available to add Postgiro number and Bankgiro number (Swedish payment methods).";s:4:"link";s:119:"https://www.woothemes.com/products/postgirobankgiro-gateway/?utm_source=product&utm_medium=upsell&utm_campaign=wcaddons";s:5:"price";s:9:"&#36;0.00";}i:66;O:8:"stdClass":5:{s:5:"title";s:16:"CCAvenue Gateway";s:5:"image";s:0:"";s:7:"excerpt";s:125:"This is the CCAvenue payment gateway for WooCommerce. Allows you to use CCAvenue payment gateway with the WooCommerce plugin.";s:4:"link";s:111:"https://www.woothemes.com/products/ccavenue-gateway/?utm_source=product&utm_medium=upsell&utm_campaign=wcaddons";s:5:"price";s:9:"&#36;0.00";}i:67;O:8:"stdClass":5:{s:5:"title";s:14:"SagePay Direct";s:5:"image";s:0:"";s:7:"excerpt";s:128:"Sagepay Direct payment gateway for Woocommerce. Once installed, you can configure this through Woocommerce Payment Gateways tab.";s:4:"link";s:109:"https://www.woothemes.com/products/sagepay-direct/?utm_source=product&utm_medium=upsell&utm_campaign=wcaddons";s:5:"price";s:9:"&#36;0.00";}i:68;O:8:"stdClass":5:{s:5:"title";s:12:"Ewire Direct";s:5:"image";s:0:"";s:7:"excerpt";s:105:"The Ewire Payment Module makes it possible for your WooCommerce store to accept payment from scandinavia.";s:4:"link";s:107:"https://www.woothemes.com/products/ewire-direct/?utm_source=product&utm_medium=upsell&utm_campaign=wcaddons";s:5:"price";s:9:"&#36;0.00";}i:69;O:8:"stdClass":5:{s:5:"title";s:17:"Robokassa Gateway";s:5:"image";s:0:"";s:7:"excerpt";s:104:"Allow customers on your WooCommerce powered online store to check out via the Russian Robokassa gateway.";s:4:"link";s:112:"https://www.woothemes.com/products/robokassa-gateway/?utm_source=product&utm_medium=upsell&utm_campaign=wcaddons";s:5:"price";s:9:"&#36;0.00";}i:70;O:8:"stdClass":5:{s:5:"title";s:16:"Postepay Gateway";s:5:"image";s:0:"";s:7:"excerpt";s:83:"Allow customers on your WooCommerce powered online store to check out via Postepay.";s:4:"link";s:111:"https://www.woothemes.com/products/postepay-gateway/?utm_source=product&utm_medium=upsell&utm_campaign=wcaddons";s:5:"price";s:9:"&#36;0.00";}i:71;O:8:"stdClass":5:{s:5:"title";s:15:"Custom Statuses";s:5:"image";s:0:"";s:7:"excerpt";s:62:"This plugin allows you to create custom orders in WooCommerce.";s:4:"link";s:110:"https://www.woothemes.com/products/custom-statuses/?utm_source=product&utm_medium=upsell&utm_campaign=wcaddons";s:5:"price";s:9:"&#36;0.00";}i:72;O:8:"stdClass":5:{s:5:"title";s:24:"Custom Product Tabs Lite";s:5:"image";s:0:"";s:7:"excerpt";s:129:"Allows a custom product tab to be added to product view pages with arbitrary content, which may contain text, html or shortcodes.";s:4:"link";s:119:"https://www.woothemes.com/products/custom-product-tabs-lite/?utm_source=product&utm_medium=upsell&utm_campaign=wcaddons";s:5:"price";s:9:"&#36;0.00";}i:73;O:8:"stdClass":5:{s:5:"title";s:9:"Cart2Cart";s:5:"image";s:0:"";s:7:"excerpt";s:184:"Cart2Cart is a service which migrates product / customer / order data from many other eCommerce platforms into WooCommerce. Perfect if you''re looking to make the switch to WooCommerce!";s:4:"link";s:104:"https://www.woothemes.com/products/cart2cart/?utm_source=product&utm_medium=upsell&utm_campaign=wcaddons";s:5:"price";s:9:"&#36;0.00";}i:74;O:8:"stdClass":5:{s:5:"title";s:20:"WPML for WooCommerce";s:5:"image";s:0:"";s:7:"excerpt";s:107:"This ''glue'' plugin makes it possible to run fully multilingual e-commerce sites using WooCommerce and WPML.";s:4:"link";s:115:"https://www.woothemes.com/products/wpml-for-woocommerce/?utm_source=product&utm_medium=upsell&utm_campaign=wcaddons";s:5:"price";s:9:"&#36;0.00";}i:75;O:8:"stdClass":5:{s:5:"title";s:14:"Affiliates Pro";s:5:"image";s:0:"";s:7:"excerpt";s:147:"Provides an affiliate management system for sellers, shops and developers, who want to increase sales with their own affiliate program immediately.";s:4:"link";s:109:"https://www.woothemes.com/products/affiliates-pro/?utm_source=product&utm_medium=upsell&utm_campaign=wcaddons";s:5:"price";s:10:"&#36;59.00";}i:76;O:8:"stdClass":5:{s:5:"title";s:15:"Product Compare";s:5:"image";s:0:"";s:7:"excerpt";s:130:"Add a Compare Products Feature to all of your products on you WooCommerce site today with the WooCommerce Compare Products plugin.";s:4:"link";s:110:"https://www.woothemes.com/products/product-compare/?utm_source=product&utm_medium=upsell&utm_campaign=wcaddons";s:5:"price";s:9:"&#36;0.00";}i:77;O:8:"stdClass":5:{s:5:"title";s:17:"Product Video Tab";s:5:"image";s:0:"";s:7:"excerpt";s:111:"Easily add a unique video tab to your product pages. Perfect if you have video demonstrations of your products.";s:4:"link";s:112:"https://www.woothemes.com/products/product-video-tab/?utm_source=product&utm_medium=upsell&utm_campaign=wcaddons";s:5:"price";s:9:"&#36;0.00";}i:78;O:8:"stdClass":5:{s:5:"title";s:9:"Piggy Pro";s:5:"image";s:0:"";s:7:"excerpt";s:137:"Piggy is an awesome, mobile web app that taps straight into WooCommerce and gives you your latest sales data on your mobile in real-time.";s:4:"link";s:104:"https://www.woothemes.com/products/piggy-pro/?utm_source=product&utm_medium=upsell&utm_campaign=wcaddons";s:5:"price";s:9:"&#36;0.00";}i:79;O:8:"stdClass":5:{s:5:"title";s:18:"Grid / List Toggle";s:5:"image";s:0:"";s:7:"excerpt";s:136:"Adds a Grid / List toggle to your product archives allowing users to, you guessed it, toggle between grid / list views of your products.";s:4:"link";s:111:"https://www.woothemes.com/products/grid-list-toggle/?utm_source=product&utm_medium=upsell&utm_campaign=wcaddons";s:5:"price";s:9:"&#36;0.00";}i:80;O:8:"stdClass":5:{s:5:"title";s:13:"WP Lister Pro";s:5:"image";s:0:"";s:7:"excerpt";s:58:"List your products on eBay and keep your inventory in sync";s:4:"link";s:104:"https://www.woothemes.com/products/wp-lister/?utm_source=product&utm_medium=upsell&utm_campaign=wcaddons";s:5:"price";s:11:"&#36;129.00";}i:81;O:8:"stdClass":5:{s:5:"title";s:13:"Smart Manager";s:5:"image";s:0:"";s:7:"excerpt";s:124:"Smart Manager is a unique, revolutionary tool that gives you the power to efficiently manage products, customers and orders.";s:4:"link";s:108:"https://www.woothemes.com/products/smart-manager/?utm_source=product&utm_medium=upsell&utm_campaign=wcaddons";s:5:"price";s:10:"&#36;97.00";}}}', 'no');
